actions.message:
/bank help - **Your Here Right Now!**
/bank details - Get your balance/wallet and more details here.
/bank transfer @usermention (amount) - Transfer money with this command.
/bank withdrawl - Add money to your **Wallet Card** from your bank account's money.
/bank deposit - Depoist money from your **Wallet Card** to your bank account.
actions.name: Add Embed Field

actions.message:
**Wallet Card**
Your wallet card is a prepaid type card, meaning you need to load money onto it.
You also should take money off of it for safe keeping.
**Debt**
Wallet cards can occur debt, debt is a serious problem and you should pay it off.
Debt's will also affect your wallet rating, Debt can occur when you go over the wallet card's amount.

actions.message:
Welcome to the admin menu help!
Please note that these commands will only work if you have the proper admin privallages...
***You may have also encountered this help menu from improperly doing a command.***
actions.name: Set Embed Description

actions.message:
***Commands that can be used to adjust a user's bank account***
/configbank @mentionuser removedebt - Remove all debt and remove all flags from user
/configbank @mentionuser addbankmoney (amount) - Give a user an entered ammount.
/configbank @mentionuser rembankmoney (amount) - Remove an entered ammount from the user
actions.name: Add Embed Field

actions.message:
***Admin Commands that can be used to control a user's wallet***
/configbank @mentionuser ratingadd (amount) - Add a given wallet rating amount to user. (Cap at 100 and lowest 0)
/configbank @mentionuser ratingrem (amount) - Remove's a given wallet rating amount to user.
/configbank @mentionuser addmoney (amount) - Give a user an entered ammount.
/configbank @mentionuser remmoney (amount) - Remove an entered ammount from the user
actions.name: Add Embed Field

actions.message:
***General Admin Command for the system itself***
/configbank changeprefix (prefix) - Add a custom prefix for the system, Default is **$**
actions.name: Add Embed Field
